px" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1635831014855" data-id="1635831014855"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1759306487748" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1759306487748"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><strong>Description:</strong></span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><i>"Can you hear the enchanted forest whispering your name, its glow shimmering just beyond the trees?"<br></i></span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br>Step into the enchanting world of the <strong>limited-edition</strong> Sylvan Glow Advent Calendar. Korean Skincare invites you on a magical stroll beneath dreamy blossoms and twinkling canopies, where every step reveals a hidden surprise. Inside, you’ll find <strong>26 full-size products</strong> and <strong>5 fairy-sized extras</strong>, carefully chosen to delight every skin type and every step of your routine, from skincare to makeup and hair care.</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">From K-Beauty staples to hidden gems, this collection is <strong>worth over £485</strong>. It’s the perfect opportunity to elevate your skincare ritual at an <strong>unbeatable price</strong>. We hope you enjoy the Sylvan Glow journey we’ve lovingly crafted for you.</span></p><p></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><strong>This Advent Calendar contains:</strong></span><br>🌿&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><strong>26</strong> full-size products & <strong>5</strong>&nbsp;minis&nbsp;<a href="#e-1759306487690-1" class=""><i>(Click here for spoilers)</i></a></span><br>🌿&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">A pocket book containing all product information, including how to use, ingredient lists and manufacturer information<br></span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><strong>Recommended for:</strong> All skin types</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><strong>How to use:</strong></span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">🌲 Open the pages of the giant Sylvan Glow book to begin your journey.</span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">🌲 Starting on the 1st of December, open a numbered box every day until Christmas.</span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">🌲 Use your Sylvan Guide along the way for product details, usage tips, and full ingredient lists.</span><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1759306487732" class="gf_row gf_equal-height gf_row-gap-10" data-icon="gpi